orkers former president bill clinton visited a west elm showroom after the company spent nearly that amount in the first year of the agreement in  the company made a pledge at the clinton global initiative annual meeting to expand its fair trade certified product offerings in  pottery barn collaborated with designer ken fulk to introduce the companys first major designer produced collection the collection includes  pieces of furniture accessories and tableware in august  williamssonoma hosted kris jenner at the grand reopening of its store in the commons at calabasas jenner attended the event with daughter khloe kardashian and signed copies of her cookbook in the kitchen with kris see alsoedit san francisco bay area portal companies portal charles e williams w howard lester rejuvenation referencesedit  corporate information business profile williamssonoma inc retrieved november     shopping catalogs making a comeback cbs news march   retrieved november     executive biographies williamssonoma inc retrieved november     a b c d e wsm summary for williamssonoma inc common st yahoo finance financeyahoocom february   retrieved november     williamssonoma inc  annual report pdf williamssonoma inc  p  retrieved november     a b lee thomas april   williamssonoma is americas best retailer — online and in store san francisco chronicle retrieved november     flynn ryan may   williamssonoma whips up new strategy seattle times retrieved november     laura alber will become ceo of williamssonoma in may furniture today january   retrieved november     a b c frojo renée november   williamssonoma accelerating global growth san francisco business times retrieved november     a b williamssonoma inc company profile hoovers retrieved november     williamssonoma retail merchandiser magazine retrieved november     a b jordan michele anna september   the comeback kid sonoma magazine retrieved november     a new source for cookware smithsonian national museum of american history retrieved 