re and is quoted as saying i knew this was something that wasn’t found in america but thought people would want shortly after returning home he formulated a plan to import french cooking and serving equipment into america and converted his store into a cookware shop in  williamssonoma was founded selling professional and restaurantquality kitchenware for home use leading to founder chuck williams being recognized as one of the titans of the american food revolution in  at the suggestion of customers williams relocated the store to san francisco the store quickly became a destination with culinary figures such as julia child and james beard becoming customers of the flagship location in  along with—and at the suggestion of—regular customer jackie mallorca williams began publishing a mail order catalog to expand his business beyond the san francisco bay area at the suggestion of customer and friend edward marcus of dallasbased neiman marcus williams decided to expand the company and formed the corporation williamssonoma inc in  the second williamssonoma store opened on rodeo drive in beverly hills in  the same year williamssonoma introduced the cuisinart food processor to the american market through its stores and catalog williams decided to sell his share of the company in  to w howard lester an oklahoma entrepreneur and businessman james mcmahan williams maintained an ownership interest and guided the selection of merchandise and the production of the catalog lester took an active role as president and chief executive while mcmahan was the company director at the time williamssonoma had revenues of  million  to edit williamssonoma inc had its initial public offering in july  one million shares were offered on the otc market  a share at end of  the company was generating over  million in sales in september  williamssonoma acquired pottery barn from gap the acquisition included pottery barns  housewares stores located in california connecticut new jersey and new york for  million the companys expansion led to the opening of its first distribution center in memphis tennessee in  williamssonoma inc is one of the largest proprietary distributors in the memphis area with  million square feet of distribution space from  to  williamssonoma inc grew by an average of  stores per year bringing the total locations to over  stores in the us the company partnered with timelife books in  to release its first series of williamssonoma kitchen library cookbooks it was listed on the new york stock exchange starting in  while sales reached  billion for the first time the following year williamssonoma inc launched its ecommerce website and bridal registry the company also launched pottery barn kids a spinoff of pottery barn that specializes in home furnishings for children  to presentedit the west elm brand was launched in  with the release of a catalog the following year the brand opened its first store the pottery barn brand further expanded with the launch of pbteen in early  in  williamssonoma entered into an agreement with the cbs news weekday program the early show to broadcast a segment the minute cooking school which presented cooking techniques styles and recipes the special weekly series was televised from williamssonomas east coast flagship store at the shops at columbus circle in new york citys time warner center this was followed by the debut of upscale williamssonoma home in  pottery barn extended its merchandising with the introduction of the pottery barn bed  bath and pottery barn kids in manhattan by  williamssonoma inc was operating  stores with an annual revenue of over  billion in may  lester retired and laura alber was named ceo of the umbrella organization previously alber joined the company in  she was active in building the pottery barn catalog and the development and launch of pottery barn kids and pbteen in november  the company acquired portland oregonbased rejuvenation inc a manufacturer and direct marketer of light fixtures and hardware with stores in portland seattle and los angeles the company launched a lifestyle brand offering personalized products mark and graham in november  williamssonoma opened a store at the site of its original location in sonoma california in  williamssonoma founder chuck williams celebrated his th birthday on the stores opening on october   the companys ecommerce sales were approximately  percent of williamssonoma incs revenue of the first quarter of  the company maintains over  stores in north america australia the middle east and the united kingdom west elm hotelsedit this section reads like a press release or a news article andor is entirely based on routine coverage please expand this article with properly sourced content to meet wikipedias quality standards event notability guideline andor encyclopedic content policy january  through the west elm brand the company is launching west elm hotels the joint venture will be done with ddk which is a hospitality management and development company the joint venture is expected to launch properties in secondary markets such as detroit minneapolis savannah georgia charlotte and indianapolis the properties are projected to open in q  the company is expanding into this new market in light of  consecutive quarters of double digit comparative growth the properties will reflect the local design elements and cuisine and culture from the region further artwork for the common areas and rooms will be commissioned from local artists in a twist hotel patrons will be able to buy the furniture used in the hotels online the west elm hotel brand will compete in the boutique hotel market which the company says is what consumer are demanding customers want unique experiences rather than standardization from hotel operators boutique hotel management is ddk’s specialty and core competency ddks founding and current principals have developed and currently operate more than  properties globally according to str a data and analytics company there is room for growth in the boutique hotel market despite the market growing  over the past six years the total number of boutique hotels only represent  of the total hotel room market supply employees were able to test out the rooms that will be built in the hotels in a brooklyn warehouse cigarette butts and soda as well as other substances were dumped and tested on the fabrics to check for quality the company will choose to use dim lighting in the hallway as it has shown that people are quieter when it’s dark international presenceedit in october  the company opened its first international stores in toronto canada in  the company opened pottery barn and west elm stores at plaza las americas in hato rey puerto rico a district of the capital san juan in  williamssonoma inc partnered with mh alshaya co to launch pottery barn and pottery barn kids franchise operations in the middle east the first williamssonoma brand store outside of north america opened in kuwait in  along with west elm at the avenues mall the largest shopping center in kuwait the company also opened four stores williamssonoma pottery barn pottery barn kids and west elm in australia as the first retail locations outside of north america owned and operated by williamssonoma inc the company opened its first store in the united kingdom in  with the launch of its west elm location in london williamssonoma signed a franchise agreement in  to begin opening stores and operating its ecommerce sites for six of its brands in mexico in the same year the company also opened pottery barn and pottery barn kids stores with a franchise partner in the philippines brandsedit under the umbrella organization of williamssonoma inc the companys brands are williamssonoma upscale products for the kitchen and home pottery barn home furnishings west elm stylized as west elm modern housewares pottery barn kids stylized as pottery barn kids home furnishings for children pbteen home furnishings for young adults williamssonoma home upscale home furnishings rejuvenation house parts and home furnishing mark and graham monogrammed gifts in popular cultureedit williamssonomas stores and gift registries have been referenced to on television shows including sex and the city season  episode  bay of married pigs american dad season  episode  when a stan loves a woman dr katz professional therapist season  episode  used car frasier mike tyson mysteries and friends williamssonoma products have been featured numerous times on the oprah winfrey shows oprahs favorite things specials including williamssonoma home bedding  williamssonomas croissants   and  williamssonomas melamine mixing bowls measuring cups and measuring spoons  perfect ending cupcakes and brevilles ikon panini press sold by williamssonoma  and williamssonomas waring popcorn maker  in the film the muse all the kitchen supplies used to manufacture the wives cookies were purchased at williamssonoma in the musical dear edwina one song references williams and sonoma as being people that sing along with the fairy forkmother to teach a chef how to set a table in  pbteen announced a collaboration with burton snowboards the collection included bedding lighting and decor the west elm brand is active with the clinton global initiative and in  agreed to invest  million on hand made goods from us and abroad to sell in its stores over the course of two years the collaborations were aimed to positively impact over  artisan workers former president bill clinton visited a west elm showroom after the company spent nearly that amount in the first year of the agreement in  the company made a pledge at the clinton global initiative annual meeting to expand its fair trade certified product offerings in  pottery barn collaborated with designer ken fulk to introduce the companys first major designer produced collection the collection includes  pieces of furniture accessories and tableware in august  williamssonoma hosted kris jenner at the grand reopening of its store in the commons at calabasas jenner attended the event with daughter khloe kardashian and signed copies of her cookbook in the kitchen with kris see alsoedit san francisco bay area portal companies portal charles e williams w howard lester rejuvenation referencesedit  corporate information business profile williamssonoma inc retrieved november     shopping catalogs making a comeback cbs news march   retrieved november     executive biographies williamssonoma inc retrieved november     a b c d e wsm summary for williamssonoma inc common st yahoo finance financeyahoocom february   retrieved november     williamssonoma inc  annual report pdf williamssonoma inc  p  retrieved november     a b lee thomas april   williamssonoma is americas best retailer — online and in store san francisco chronicle retrieved november     flynn ryan may   williamssonoma whips up new strategy seattle times retrieved november     laura alber will become ceo of williamssonoma in may furniture today january   retrieved november     a b c frojo renée november   williamssonoma accelerating global growth san francisco business times retrieved november     a b williamssonoma inc company profile hoovers retrieved november     williamssonoma retail merchandiser magazine retrieved november     a b jordan michele anna september   the comeback kid sonoma magazine retrieved november     a new source for cookware smithsonian national museum of american history retrieved november     a b fletcher janet october   williamssonoma returns home to celebrate heritage sfgate retrieved november     allen gary j albala ken  the business of food encyclopedia of the food and drink industries abcclio p  isbn  retrieved november     a b c williamssonoma inc history international directory of company histories  retrieved november     kamp david  the united states of arugula how we became a gourmet nation broadway books p  isbn  retrieved november     chuck williams williamssonoma retrieved novemb