 and in other major cities across south korea soon” this october williamssonoma inc and livart will open a fivestory flagship store in nonhyundong seoul the superstore will include pottery barn pottery barn kids and west elm and will represent the first time three williamssonoma inc brands are offered in a single standalone location an additional williams sonoma store will be opened in the hyundai city mall daegu branch in the latter half of this year   webinars running with the big boys ecommerce tools for the midmarkethow to unlock omnichannel profitabilitya marketplace guide to  holiday successthe perfect omnichannel order myths realities and best practicesthe amazon first party p survival guidelatest research successful ecommerce packaging sustainable and protectivemcm outlook  ecommerce growth in double digitsnew digital fulfillment strategies help meet customer expectationshow top brands deliver great customer experiencesselecting the right wms for your current and future needsblogs how to level the playing field as amazon eats the world ecommerce logistics predictions for  tips for improving picking productivitymaking the most of the omnichannel customer experiencehow big box retailers can create a worldclass experience in retail openingsbackup  williamssonoma inc customer care centers available jobs in customer care centers engaging with customers by phone email and live chat customer care center associates deliver worldclass service every day and serve as a critical link between our customer and our product customer care center associates have strong communication skills a thirst for knowledge about our brands and a passion for the retail industry if you are enthusiastic about helping customers create their dream homes providing everything from advice on color palettes and price points to suggestions on product use and care check out the jobs listed here my accountopeningsbelow is a list of current job openings at williamssonoma inc customer care centers pl