arties in a number of countries in the middle east the philippines and mexico by the end of this year williamssonoma inc will be represented at more than  international retail locations” said ronald young executive vice president global of williams–sonoma inc “as we begin our partnership with livart opening our first four stores of many to come in south korea we look forward to the tremendous opportunity of continuing our global expansion” “the first williamssonoma inc store openings bring a big change to the domestic home furnishings market in south korea” said hwaeung kim representative director and chief executive officer of hyundai livart furniture co ltd “our partnership with williamssonoma inc helps us bring the best quality and differentiated design offerings to customers and we are looking forward to opening additional stores in seoul and in other major cities across south korea soon” this october williamssonoma inc and livart will open a fivestory flagship store in nonhyundong seoul the superstore will include pottery barn pottery barn kids and west elm and will represent the first time three williamssonoma inc brands are offered in a single standalone location an additional williams sonoma store will be opened in the hyundai city mall daegu branch in the latter half of this year   webinars running with the big boys ecommerce tools for the midmarkethow to unlock omnichannel profitabilitya marketplace guide to  holiday successthe perfect omnichannel order myths realities and best practicesthe amazon first party p survival guidelatest research successful ecommerce packaging sustainable and protectivemcm outlook  ecommerce growth in double digitsnew digital fulfillment strategies help meet customer expectationshow top brands deliver great customer experiencesselecting the right wms for your current and future needsblogs how to level the playing field as amazon eats the world ecommerce logistics predictions for  tips for improving picking productivitymaking the